Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:16.02,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Amazing! It happened so quickly, \Nmy eyes couldn't keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.02,0:00:19.81,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, I {\i1}have{\i0} been beating up \Nslimes for 300 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:24.81,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,And how many slimes did you defeat \Neach day to get so strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:27.81,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Like... 25?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:31.92,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Oh, but I have an ability that \Nincreases the experience I earn,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,so it actually comes out to about 50 a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:36.10,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,It sounds like you had it easier I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:39.59,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I thought you would say you worked \Nhard enough to sweat blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.78,0:00:42.84,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Laika, you need to throw away \Nthose kinds of thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:44.67,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:47.90,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Because if you're working \Nhard enough to sweat blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.90,0:00:51.00,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,it means you know people are watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:56.90,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,So you've probably been using that \Nexpression with the intention of boasting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:00:58.76,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Wh-When you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:02.56,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Anyway, you just keep steadily \Nplugging along every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:06.09,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Looking at any activity that way \Nmakes it easier to keep it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:08.08,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,and you'll level up naturally along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:10.81,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Such meaningful, priceless words...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:14.54,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I will fully dedicate myself to \Nreaching your level one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:18.46,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's not like the slimes are \Never gonna try to get revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:20.93,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Let's just keep mowing them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:24.88,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Witch of the Highlands...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:27.29,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,You shall pay dearly.
