Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:07.94,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa, I shall prepare \Nour meal for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.53,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, I guess I'll leave you to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:13.23,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I didn't know dragons could cook, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:16.82,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Of course. Dragons are \None of the noble races.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:19.03,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Cooking is but a simple task!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:19.75,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Dun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:20.56,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Dun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:21.41,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Dun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:23.01,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Da-dun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:24.29,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,This is my finest creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:26.47,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Please, help yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.47,0:03:27.65,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:30.79,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I do enjoy omelettes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:34.05,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But I think you might've \Nused a few too many eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:36.19,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This is way too much for two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.68,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:40.29,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I just can't cast aside \Nmy values as a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:44.21,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I see. Well, let's eat \Nit before it gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:45.77,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:48.03,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:54.77,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:57.43,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I gotta be honest! You're fantastic, Laika!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:59.25,Main,Raika,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:01.90,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll make it every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:05.41,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Nah, we'll rotate. I'll do \Nmy share of cooking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:08.74,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You can show off your skills \Nwhen it's your day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:11.16,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll give it my all, then, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:18.89,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Laika, if there's anything you want to \Nknow about the life we live, just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:22.51,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Well... there is one thing, \Nabout that village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:23.88,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,About Flatta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:27.91,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Yes. Its magic defense is extremely weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:32.28,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Just one evil mage could reduce \Nit to a sea of flames in moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:35.93,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yeah, but wouldn't that be \Ntrue pretty much anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.78,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,It's not only that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:40.87,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,It has no measures in place to \Ndeal with land-based attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:44.86,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,If large monsters attacked en masse, \Nit wouldn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:46.46,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I think you might be overthinking this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:51.46,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,But the news of your strength just \Nrecently became widely known, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:57.55,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Some vile fiend could take the whole \Nvillage hostage just to get rid of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:02.93,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I get it... But it's not like I \Ncan guard them around the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:07.83,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,But there is something we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.80,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,A DIY barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:15.98,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,One of your many skills \Nis Create Magic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:19.19,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,You can use it to make a \Nbarrier around the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.72,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,If you want it to have a long-term effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:23.78,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,the best way is to draw a magic circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:27.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wow, you dragons know a \Nlot about magic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:31.08,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I learned about it when I went \Nto an all-girls school...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.33,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,All-girls school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.51,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,All right, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:36.16,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'll give it a shot, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.35,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You who have wicked hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:43.13,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,be caught in this net and \Nbecome incapacitated!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:52.66,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.68,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Yes, they should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:57.78,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:06:01.19,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I don't know... I just have \Nthis foreboding feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:08.96,Main,Old,0,0,0,,This thief who entered the \Nvillage suddenly can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:12.11,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa, it's already working!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:13.96,Main,Old,0,0,0,,What could have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:17.70,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa put a barrier over \Nthe village just moments ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.96,Main,Old,0,0,0,,Oh! At last, the debate over \Nvillage safety measures
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:24.22,Main,Old,0,0,0,,that has plagued us for \Nmany long years is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:26.19,Main,Old,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:30.32,Main,Old,0,0,0,,Thanks to the great witch, \Nthis village will be even more peaceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:34.01,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Please, Headman, that's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.23,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,If you're going to praise someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.02,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You should praise Laika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:38.86,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:43.77,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It was my pupil, Laika the Dragon, \Nwho suggested putting up the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:47.81,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,N-No, it was none other than Lady \NAzusa who erected the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.20,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I did nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.16,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.86,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The dragon you defeated before, Great Witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:56.65,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yeah. Laika became my pupil a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:07:00.12,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,She's a very nice, thoughtful girl, \Nso treat her well, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:04.93,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,My name is Laika. \NIt's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:07.94,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,No wonder! The Great Witch's \Npupil is bound to be special!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.78,Main - Top,Guy,0,0,0,,This village is gonna be \Neven nicer to live in now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:10.88,Main,Lady,0,0,0,,Having a good-hearted dragon on our \Nside gives us the strength of an army!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:15.92,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're here now, Laika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.30,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You do such a good job with the chores,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:19.90,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,and you make such tasty meals for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:24.32,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I have also learned a great \Ndeal from you, Lady Azusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:33.55,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,I hope we can keep living \Nthis easy life forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.38,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,A little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Hi there. Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:56.68,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I've been dying to see you, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.70,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:02.88,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:04.60,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Do we have a visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:08.10,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I'm Falfa! I came to see my mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.41,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa has a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:13.35,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,No, I don't! This kid's mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.59,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I'm not mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.62,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,So your name's Falfa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:22.55,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,"Mama" is what you'd call the woman \Nwho gave birth to you and raised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:24.78,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,You gave birth to me, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:29.17,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,They call you the \NWitch of the Highlands, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.46,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I know 'cause my little \Nsister looked into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:33.83,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You have a little sister, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:37.87,Main - Top,Laika,0,0,0,,W-Well, it does make sense that you'd have \Na love child or two after living 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:40.72,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I have learned so much from you, Lady Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.74,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You don't need to learn that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:44.95,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Anyway, Mama, there's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.85,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,My little sister's trying to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:51.27,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Someone wants to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:53.36,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,This just turned into a suspense story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:56.75,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I don't want you to die, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:57.86,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:02.25,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa, we should let her in \Nand hear what she has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.49,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:07.21,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Want to come in and have \Nsome cookies, Falfa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.64,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'd love some!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:14.42,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Now that I look closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:17.67,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,she does kinda look like \Nme when I was little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:19.72,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Actually, no, she doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.74,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.72,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:27.61,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,So... can you tell me your \Nlittle sister's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:28.72,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,It's Shalsha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:32.25,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Then is this Shalsha... my child, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.79,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:37.70,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,But why would she want to kill Lady Azusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.94,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,I think she's holding a grudge against Mama,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.15,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,since Mama killed her and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:46.25,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,My slow life just took an occultish turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:48.59,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I still don't understand all the details,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:52.75,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,but in any case, I believe we need \Nto protect you from this Shalsha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.17,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:57.81,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Falfa, do you know how she \Nmight try to attack me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:59.66,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:03.05,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Shalsha was always studying \NSmite Evil magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:04.42,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Smite Evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:09.66,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Isn't that a really powerful type of \Nmagic that only works on certain races?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:11.06,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Yes, including...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.18,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.32,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,orcs,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.91,Main,Laike,0,0,0,,and elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:18.99,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,The more specific its target is, \Nthe stronger its effects are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:24.63,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,So if you said, "Smite Evil: Living Thing," \Nit wouldn't do much at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:29.84,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Yes, but it's said that it takes \Nseveral decades to learn the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:35.47,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,How long have you two been alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:38.79,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Hmm... About 50 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:42.17,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Which means they're not just normal humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:46.11,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,In that case, there's a chance she \Ncould be a powerful magic user.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:50.38,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But what Smite Evil spell \Nwould specifically target me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:55.16,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Shalsha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:03.58,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I've finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.92,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's Shalsha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.55,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,What an ominous aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:08.19,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Shalsha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:10.08,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Don't be mean to Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:13.51,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I will avenge my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:17.73,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Shalsha, there's no way \NI could have killed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:18.08,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:23.63,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,You have killed countless slimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:28.44,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Huh? Slimes? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:34.46,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,The two of us are made up of the \Nsouls of the slimes that you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.36,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,We're basically slime spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.94,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Slime spirits?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:42.03,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I will kill you so that \Nall slimes can rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:46.05,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,But there's no way I can fight a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:50.03,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa, why don't you use your \Ntornado magic and see what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:54.67,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,If she's a spirit, there's no risk of \Nkilling her with a little tornado.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.54,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we're not \Ngetting anywhere now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.29,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Might as well try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:04.38,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wind, be my servant and \Nblow with all your might!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.30,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Tornado...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:07.63,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:12.20,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,That's the Smite Evil spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:15.35,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,But how can it be powerful enough \Nto erase Lady Azusa's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:18.16,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Many years of training to defeat you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:20.67,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,allowed me to perfect this spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:23.84,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Smite Evil: Witch of the Highlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.95,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,"Smite Evil: Witch of the Highlands"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:28.72,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,O-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:32.34,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,The more specific Smite Evil's target \Nis, the stronger its effects are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:35.28,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,If it's specific enough to \Ntarget Lady Azusa alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:38.64,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,It will negate any magic you try to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:40.05,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:43.89,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Go ahead. Use any magic spell you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.64,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Red flame...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:51.77,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Blue flame...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:56.30,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Black flame! Become my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:02.44,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Y-You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:03.69,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Shalsha's been
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:08.97,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,saving up her strength for this day \Never since she was born 50 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.62,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Even though a spell that consumes \Nas much mana as Smite Evil
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.99,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,only lasts an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.24,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's so ineffective!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.99,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:19.33,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,She's only after me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:23.05,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,so Laika and Falfa won't be harmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.18,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,In my past life,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:28.03,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,I died of exhaustion when I couldn't \Nescape the corporate slave lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.56,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,So I know this feeling firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.05,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,When times are tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.32,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:35.74,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Magic, disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.09,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.57,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Whoa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:44.94,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:46.38,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Hey! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:50.55,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,If I wasn't a level 99 witch, \NI might've broken some bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:52.27,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,You will not escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:56.53,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I will kill you, just like \Nyou killed all those slimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:58.83,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:13:59.29,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:03.04,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:06.17,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Maybe it's high time I paid the piper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:08.72,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,I've lived for 300 years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.33,0:14:12.72,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I'm glad I met you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:14.71,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:16.44,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Prepare to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:17.60,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:20.89,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Laika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:23.56,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I will not allow you to \Ncome one step closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:29.20,Eyecatch,Title,0,0,0,,I've Been Killing {\c&HE4AE06&}Slimes\N{\c&H313536&}for {\c&HE4AE06&}300 Years {\c&H313536&}and\N{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Maxed Out {\c&H313536&\3c&HFFFFFF&}My {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7600D0&}Level
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:32.83,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Step aside, Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:36.45,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I will not! I have a duty \Nto protect my master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.21,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Then I will not hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.22,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Stop, Laika!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.84,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Dragon Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:50.43,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.59,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Poke, poke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:58.76,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa, she has lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.77,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I... have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:01.92,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.11,Main,Echo,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1000)}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:04.36,Main,Echo,0,0,0,,{\fs20\fad(1,1000)}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.34,Main,Echo,0,0,0,,{\fs16\fad(1,900)}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:06.77,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,My little sister, Shalsha,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:09.71,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,focused too specifically \Non magic targeting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:12.03,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,so I guess she's really \Nweak against anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:13.78,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What a little klutz!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.28,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Oh, Shalsha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.29,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.79,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You're in my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:22.97,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Witch of the Highlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:25.87,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You were unconscious after losing to Laika,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:27.29,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,so we brought you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:29.21,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I asked for no such pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:31.48,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Smite Evil: Witch of the Highlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:41.27,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I think you already used up all your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:45.04,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You won't be able to use Smite \NEvil again for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:46.46,Narration - Top,SFX,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:52.33,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,But... I have lived solely to get revenge \Non the Witch of the Highlands...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:55.24,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,What has my entire life been for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:58.44,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Actually, isn't it a good \Nthing that I'm still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:03.04,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,If I was dead, you'd have \Nno reason to live anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:05.18,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,but as long as I don't die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:08.46,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,you can still have your goal \Nto get revenge on me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:12.33,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,One could put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:16.30,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama took care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.00,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Why would you do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:22.48,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well, I'm the mother who gave \Nbirth to you, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.06,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,So I can't just leave you injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:27.89,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,You could indeed be called my mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:31.13,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,but you are still the one \Nwho killed the slimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:35.55,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Shalsha, stop being so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:36.57,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:39.71,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,It's nature's way for slimes \Nand humans to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.29,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,No matter how much you hate Mama,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:45.74,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,all kinds of people around the \Nworld are killing slimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:49.36,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Just listen closely, and you'll \Nhear their screams, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.30,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Wow, that's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:57.94,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Anyway, you can't hold a grudge against \Neveryone who's ever killed a slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:00.10,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:02.65,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Since we were lucky enough to be born,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:05.82,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,we should think about how \Nwe can live happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:08.43,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,That'll be more fun, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:11.82,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:15.28,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,It appears this issue has been resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:18.07,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Yeah. I wasn't sure what was \Ngonna happen for a while there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.72,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,By the way, where do you two live?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:25.88,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,In a shack in the forest that \Nno one ever comes near.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.59,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Anyone else live there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:28.54,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:29.98,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:34.31,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Then you should both live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:35.30,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:37.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,There are lots of rooms here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:41.56,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Besides, it makes sense for a mother \Nand her kids to live together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:45.27,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Yeah! I wanna live with you, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:46.84,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Okay, Shalsha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:48.85,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Witch of the Highlands...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:52.94,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Don't call me that. Make it \Nsound like we're family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.08,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,M-Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:59.83,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I will live with you, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:01.56,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, then, it's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:05.62,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Lady Azusa, why don't we have \Na welcome party tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:06.72,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:10.26,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, let's all go buy stuff for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:10.71,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:11.67,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:12.84,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:21.88,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,By the way, what did you two \Ndo before you came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:23.99,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,We got rid of evil slimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.40,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Evil slimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:30.65,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,There are both good slimes and evil slimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:35.15,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Um, I just want to make sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:37.65,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,It's okay to kill slimes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.63,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Sure, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:41.87,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,It never bothered me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:44.17,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,and Shalsha seems to be okay with it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:48.32,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,The slimes of Nanterre are \Ntypically dark-colored...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:51.39,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,But the ones here are quite pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:53.91,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Light-colored slimes are evil slimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:55.23,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,They should be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:58.67,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,R-Really? How informative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:01.67,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Also, slimes have a hole \Nthat's their weak spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.97,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,You are already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:04.84,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Jab!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:07.98,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.37,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,They truly are slime spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:26.45,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's the baker, \Nand next door is the tailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:30.30,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Remember all this so you won't get \Nlost when you run errands here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:33.91,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Okay, Mama! I've got it all down pat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:35.42,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.43,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, how many of the shops on \Nthe main street can you name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.69,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,The sixth building from the village's \Nsouth entrance is Noelis Shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:43.38,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,and the next one is Meitz Dairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:46.62,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,The fifth building was a general store \Nuntil a year ago, but now it's vacant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:49.51,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,The next one, Kant's Store, \Nsells seeds and farm equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:51.69,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Oh, and the owner threw out \Ntheir back the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:53.02,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,That's too much detail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:57.74,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,What about you, Shalsha? You seemed \Nquite curious about lots of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:01.85,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,That slightly wider street \Nis the old highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:05.76,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,If you look closely, you can see \Nremnants of when it was a shrine road.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:09.43,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,The area around it used to be a \Ncheckpoint in the old kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:12.29,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,They are definitely your \Ndaughters, Lady Azusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.66,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,They're so intelligent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:17.45,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,I think this goes far beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:20.22,Main,All,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:24.74,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Big Sis Laika, this omelette is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.64,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.35,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I'm so glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.39,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,It means my extra effort was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:30.51,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:34.77,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! I've made too much again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:37.98,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Nah, our family has two more members now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:39.73,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,This is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:44.09,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What's wrong, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:45.94,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:49.49,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama, do we have to eat the celery, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:52.28,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,I don't like celery, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:56.96,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Okay, if you eat it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:59.59,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,you can have some chiffon cake later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:07.37,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Very good! You shouldn't \Nbe picky with your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:12.43,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,What? Did you leave your celery, too, Laika?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:17.69,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,A-A-Actually, there's a rule within my \Nclan that we must never eat celery!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:20.94,Main,Azusa,0,0,0,,Laika, it's not good to lie to your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:23.87,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry! I'll eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.36,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Why must celery taste like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:30.07,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:38.02,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Living my slow life alone was nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:41.77,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,but I think I prefer having a more \Nlively place to come home to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.77,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,After killing slimes for 300 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:46.52,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,I gained one pupil
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:49.05,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,and two daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:51.55,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:54.67,Main,Falfa,0,0,0,,The two of us can share a room!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:55.57,Main,Shalsha,0,0,0,,Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:57.87,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Then we can take in more family members.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:01.03,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,We have a dragon and spirits, \Nso should an elf be next?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.03,0:22:02.31,Main,Laika,0,0,0,,Or perhaps a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.54,0:22:05.33,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:10.61,Italics,Azusa,0,0,0,,I guess a slow life with a big \Nfamily is nice in its own way.
